                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=94134#94134"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Thu Jan 20, 2005 12:57 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
